text.tspan: This website was built almost entirely using SVG, and only the essential parts of HTML and CSS.
No more being constrained by the limits of HTML and CSS.
By using vector graphics programs like Inkscape, you too can design websites faster than ever, for
free, in real-time, with more creative freedom, without using website builders and other proprietary
These programs cost money to use basic features, which in my opinion should be free.
No more website builders - just clean SVG, HTML, CSS and JavaScript.
Using this approach to making websites also enables you to shift website hosts without being
locked down in the WordPress ecosystem, and also makes your websites run faster.
